 results were also determined by a simplified method using a sample pooled to be representative of the rumen outflow of undegraded feed. The respective values for RS and TR were 54.8 and 51.6 for DM and 65.8 and 78.9% for CP. This method seems to be a promising technique to estimate IED, although more studies are needed to improve its accuracy.";}s:8:"authId_i";a:5:{i:0;i:921634;i:1;i:936378;i:2;i:936379;i:3;i:921670;i:4;i:921671;}s:14:"authLastName_s";a:5:{i:0;s:9:"González";i:1;s:14:"Faría-Mármol";i:2;s:8:"Matesanz";i:3;s:10:"Rodríguez";i:4;s:5:"Alvir";}s:15:"authFirstName_s";a:5:{i:0;s:6:"Javier";i:1;s:6:"Jesús";i:2;s:8:"Bárbara";i:3;s:6:"Carlos";i:4;s:6:"María";}s:14:"authFullName_s";a:5:{i:0;s:16:"Javier González";i:1;s:21:"Jesús Faría-Mármol";i:2;s:17:"Bárbara Matesanz";i:3;s:17:"Carlos Rodríguez";i:4;s:12:"María Alvir";}s:23:"authLastNameFirstName_s";a:5:{i:0;s:16:"González Javier";i:1;s:21:"Faría-Mármol Jesús";i:2;s:17:"Matesanz Bárbara";i:3;s:17:"Rodríguez Carlos";i:4;s:12:"Alvir María";}s:26:"authIdLastNameFirstName_fs";a:5:{i:0;s:32:"921634_FacetSep_González Javier";i:1;s:37:"936378_FacetSep_Faría-Mármol Jesús";i:2;s:33:"936379_FacetSep_Matesanz Bárbara";i:3;s:33:"921670_FacetSep_Rodríguez Carlos";i:4;s:28:"921671_FacetSep_Alvir María";}s:31:"authAlphaLastNameFirstNameId_fs";a:5:{i:0;s:43:"G_AlphaSep_González Javier_FacetSep_921634";i:1;s:48:"F_AlphaSep_Faría-Mármol Jesús_FacetSep_936378";i:2;s:44:"M_AlphaSep_Matesanz Bárbara_FacetSep_936379";i:3;s:44:"R_AlphaSep_Rodríguez Carlos_FacetSep_921670";i:4;s:39:"A_AlphaSep_Alvir María_FacetSep_921671";}s:17:"authIdFullName_fs";a:5:{i:0;s:32:"921634_FacetSep_Javier González";i:1;s:37:"936378_FacetSep_Jesús Faría-Mármol";i:2;s:33:"936379_FacetSep_Bárbara Matesanz";i:3;s:33:"921670_FacetSep_Carlos Rodríguez";i:4;s:28:"921671_FacetSep_María Alvir";}s:17:"authFullNameId_fs";a:5:{i:0;s:32:"Javier González_FacetSep_921634";i:1;s:37:"Jesús Faría-Mármol_FacetSep_936378";i:2;s:33:"Bárbara Matesanz_FacetSep_936379";i:3;s: